            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am immensely pleased with the experience my 2.5-year-old son has had at Kangaroo Kids Play School. From the moment we enrolled him, the care and attention provided by the staff have been nothing short of exceptional. The individualized care each child receives ensures that every child's unique needs and preferences are catered to, making the environment feel like a second home.\n\nOne of the standout qualities of Kangaroo Kids is the immaculate cleanliness of the facilities. It is clear that the school takes great pride in maintaining a hygienic and safe environment for the children, which gives parents like myself great peace of mind.\n\nThe professionalism of the staff is evident in their interactions with both parents and children. They are not only warm and welcoming but also demonstrate a high level of expertise in early childhood education. Their dedication is reflected in the remarkable progress my son has made in such a short span of time. He has already started recognizing numbers and even spelling out simple words, a testament to the effective learning methods employed by the school.\n\nIn conclusion, Kangaroo Kids Play School has surpassed our expectations in every aspect, from individualized care to the development of foundational learning skills. I am grateful for the nurturing and stimulating environment they provide, which undoubtedly lays a strong foundation for my son's future learning journey.",
