          "reviewBody": "We must say this is the best school in Kolkata. Our son kavish is super happy with the school environment and teachers. Teachers are so caring and well trained. Every day he is learning new things. We saw a really positive change in his personality. Even though we are so happy, transportation is so smooth with pushpa mam, no homework load like other schools. He always wants to talk in English and forces us too,😁🥰",
