            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Kangaroo Kids (Newtown, Kolkata) has been an exceptional experience for my child.\nThe variety of activities provided, from creative arts to interactive play, ensures that kids are always stimulated and learning. The teachers are not only highly skilled but also genuinely caring, creating a nurturing environment that fosters growth and development.\n\nOne of the standout features is the school's flexibility in allowing parents to accompany their children during the transition phase, which has been invaluable in easing the anxiety and adjustment to the external world for both my child and me.\n\nKangaroo Kids truly excels in early childhood education, making it a top choice for parents.",
