          "reviewBody": "My granddaughter goes to Kangaroo Kids, New Town and I think it is really very good especially for beginners as I had few days of experience sitting in the classroom with my grand daughter. I saw how beautifully they teach the kids about basics of everything like alphabets, food, animals, birds and their habitats, etc with the help of modules which is really helpful for them. They make sure that the kids reach home safely and they take immense care of them during the lunch hours, making sure the kids eat the food on time and without fuss. Overall an extremely nourishing experience for my little one.",
